{
  "stem": "17337.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So that was happy times.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, they live all-- all around Poland.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] There's-- there's one who lived in the same town, in Bochnia, where I was.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One lived in Krakow.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "One lived in Tarnow.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "One lived in [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I had a uncle, too, who emigrated to-- to Brazil.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And I had aunts who lived in Tarnow and one in Szczuczyn.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Actually, there was-- there was two who lived in Tarnow and one in Szczuczyn.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "My-- my mother was the third one.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There were-- my grandfather had nine-- actually he had 11 children, by two passed away what I never knew them.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So when the-- board work out, they-- I had six uncles and three-- actually, two aunts, because my mother was the third one from [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I have [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] at least about 15 cousins because every one of them had two or three children.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I remember it very well.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was the-- the 3rd of September.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was on a Friday.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We knew that the Germans are getting closer and closer.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I remember we were in our next-door apartment together with-- with neighbors.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we spent all night there, sitting and waiting for-- for arrival of the German.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we heard the-- the-- the bombardments and-- and-- all night long.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And by daybreak, they came in-- into town.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And naturally, everybody was afraid to-- to-- to go out from-- from the home.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And that's from the beginning when it start to have the problems with the Jews.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We had to start to wear a-- white armbands with the-- with the name 'Juden' on it.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
